  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this retrospective study, the investigators examined incidence and risk factors of
      postoperative nausea and vomiting (PONV) in patients with fentanyl-based intravenous
      patient-controlled analgesia (IV-PCA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
